---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import img0 from "../assets/img0.jpg";
import img1 from "../assets/img1.jpg";
import img2 from "../assets/img2.jpg";
import img3 from "../assets/img3.jpg";
---

<div>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-red-100 to-red-200 text-white">
    <div class="container px-6 py-12 mx-auto">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-4 xl:grid-cols-5">
        <div
          class="max-w-2xl mx-auto my-8 space-y-4 text-center xl:col-span-2 xl:text-left"
        >
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-black">The Balanced Chef</h2>
          <p class="text-black">
            "Bringing you a world of flavors and wholesome recipes to inspire
            your culinary journey."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 xl:col-span-3">
          <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="grid content-center gap-4">
              <div class="p-6 rounded shadow-md bg-black bg-opacity-100">
                <p>
                  "I never knew healthy food could taste this good! The Balanced
                  Chef's recipes have transformed my meals into a delicious and
                  guilt-free experience."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-4">
                  <Image
                    src={img0}
                    alt=""
                    class="bg-center bg-cover rounded-full"
                    width={45}
                    height={45}
                  />
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Leroy Jenkins</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Food Enthusiast</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 rounded shadow-md bg-black">
                <p>
                  "The Balanced Chef's recipes have become a staple in my
                  kitchen. They are not only nutritious but also bursting with
                  flavor. I highly recommend trying their dishes!"
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-4">
                  <Image
                    src={img1}
                    alt=""
                    class="bg-center bg-cover rounded-full"
                    width={45}
                    height={45}
                  />
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Steward Masweneng</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Health Coach</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid content-center gap-4">
              <div class="p-6 rounded shadow-md bg-black">
                <p>
                  "As a busy professional, I struggled to find time to cook
                  nutritious meals. Thanks to The Balanced Chef's easy-to-follow
                  recipes, I can now prepare healthy dishes in no time. It has
                  been a game-changer for me!"
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-4">
                  <Image
                    src={img2}
                    alt=""
                    class="bg-center bg-cover rounded-full"
                    width={45}
                    height={45}
                  />
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Sophia Lee</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Marketing Executive</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 rounded shadow-md bg-black">
                <p>
                  "I've always struggled with finding healthy options that
                  actually taste good. The Balanced Chef has exceeded my
                  expectations with their flavorful and nourishing recipes. It's
                  a game-changer for anyone looking to eat well without
                  sacrificing taste!"
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-4">
                  <Image
                    src={img3}
                    alt=""
                    class="bg-center bg-cover rounded-full"
                    width={45}
                    height={45}
                  />
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Oliver Smith</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Fitness Enthusiast</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="py-4 bg-white">
    <div
      class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-gray-500 font-regular">F.A.Q</p>
        <h3
          class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-normal font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900"
        >
          Frequently Asked <span class="text-red-600">Questions</span>
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20">
        <ul class="">
          <li class="text-left mb-10">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-start mb-5">
              <div
                class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center p-3 mr-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white border-4 border-white text-xl font-semibold"
              >
                <Icon name="question" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-100 p-5 px-10 w-full flex items-center">
                <h4 class="text-md leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                  What are your opening hours?
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
              <div class="bg-red-100 p-5 px-10 w-full flex items-center">
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  The Balanced Chef is open from Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to
                  10:00 PM. On Saturdays and Sundays, we are open from 10:00 AM
                  to 11:00 PM. Please note that these hours are subject to
                  change, so it's always a good idea to check our website or
                  call us for the most up-to-date information.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center p-3 ml-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white border-4 border-white text-xl font-semibold"
              >
                <Icon name="person" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="text-left mb-10">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-start mb-5">
              <div
                class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center p-3 mr-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white border-4 border-white text-xl font-semibold"
              >
                <Icon name="question" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-100 p-5 px-10 w-full flex items-center">
                <h4 class="text-md leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                  What are the parking and public transport options?
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
              <div class="bg-red-100 p-5 px-10 w-full flex items-center">
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  The Balanced Chef provides both parking and public transport
                  options for our guests. We have a dedicated parking lot
                  available for patrons, making it convenient for those who
                  prefer to drive. Additionally, there are public transport
                  stops within walking distance of our restaurant, allowing easy
                  access for those using buses or trains. Please check our
                  website for more detailed directions and information
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center p-3 ml-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white border-4 border-white text-xl font-semibold"
              >
                <Icon name="person" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="text-left mb-10">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-start mb-5">
              <div
                class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center p-3 mr-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white border-4 border-white text-xl font-semibold"
              >
                <Icon name="question" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-100 p-5 px-10 w-full flex items-center">
                <h4 class="text-md leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                  What is your cancellation policy?
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
              <div class="bg-red-100 p-5 px-10 w-full flex items-center">
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  Our cancellation policy at The Balanced Chef allows you to
                  cancel your reservation up to 24 hours before your scheduled
                  dining time without any charges. However, for cancellations
                  made within 24 hours or no-shows, a cancellation fee may be
                  applied. We understand that unforeseen circumstances can
                  arise, so please notify us as soon as possible if you need to
                  cancel or reschedule your reservation.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center p-3 ml-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 text-white border-4 border-white text-xl font-semibold"
              >
                <Icon name="person" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
